    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/17626/" target="_blank">Take a new look on the familiar world .</a>
                <span class="pl">(蜗牛阿不思)</span>
